{"tid":577811,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【世紀合作】畢彼特與里安納度落實拍昆頓新戲 齊齊演過氣奀星","createTime":"2018-03-02T05:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T03:16:43.000Z","uid":47132,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2a10c5de0b7db23b7c67481ffc2bcf95cbe50b5a","tid":577811,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180301/large/1519875272_0931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180301%2Flarge%2F1519875272_0931.jpg&h=c3d63e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荷李活鬼才導演昆頓塔倫天奴（Quentin Tarantino）開拍「世紀殺人魔」曼森（Charles Manson）電影終於落實細節！除咗之前一直傳出嘅畢彼特（Brad Pitt）同里安納度狄卡比奧（Leonardo Dicaprio）落實參演外，角色細節亦曝光。外界之前一直估佢哋會做調查殺人案嘅探員，點知通通都錯，今次佢哋係做被殺女星莎朗蒂（Sharon Tate）嘅鄰居，亦即係2個過氣奀星！<br />\n<br />\n電影戲名叫《Once Upon a Time in Hollywood》，故事發生於1969年嘅荷李活，里安納度演嘅Rick Dalton係個過氣西部牛仔劇演員，而畢彼特演嘅Cliff Booth就仲奀，只係Rick Dalton嘅動作替身！佢哋於荷李活爭扎求存，不過剛巧就住正女星莎朗蒂隔離，亦即係曼森嘅殘殺對象！電影之前一直有開唔成嘅危機，本來投資者為Harvey Weinstein嘅電影公司，不過佢因爆出性醜聞而令電影一度中止籌備，而家最終於Sony電影公司買下版權，順利開拍。"},{"pid":"73508e6f12cf290f8adba99d152ded60b19fcf91","tid":577811,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"屌你正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de664480540eeb3393b86a317685e6501d42b90","tid":577811,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"俾一套戲既錢睇兩個影帝，唔錯，雖然我令仔D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fff901dd265af180ea9295e30ac69982796c8bb","tid":577811,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"qt個樣已經咁老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6946a3f6fad1449513ea3d4d83ecc191aeec807","tid":577811,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":